Mercedes-Benz has tried to breathe new breath into the sector with this off-roader.
Precisely because of its extraordinary characteristics, the Suv Glk ’ s presentation will also be unconventional, and will be on display in Mercedes ’ s showroom from 17 October.
Thus, the advertising drum that will accompany the appearance of the new model will also appear in a new guise, namely in the form of a 3D advertising campaign - this is a novelty in the car sector in backward Italy.
