The first phase will consist of the presentation of the car in the form of 3D glasses distributed near the Corso Como, giving the whole thing a special look: the new Suv will thus appear in its almost real dimensions as a three-dimensional model.
Indeed, the car will appear to emerge from the poster on which it is depicted.
The new Glk is then illuminated in all its details in different moments with the help of Elumina8 and then put together as a whole again.
Undoubtedly it is the concern of Mercedes to introduce with this advertisement a new kind of the car advertisement into this rather stereotype field.
But will it succeed in arousing the interest of future buyers? We will see.
